import {CREATE_EVENT, DELETE_EVENT, ALL_DELEATE_EVENT} from ',,/actions'

const events = (state, action) => {
    switch(action.type) {
        case CREATE_EVENT:
            return state
        case DELETE_EVENT:
            return state
        case ALL_DELEATE_EVENT:
            return state
        default:
            return state
    }

}

export default events
